title: After Hours: My Sister's House fundraiser
text:
Tia Gemmell Contributing photographer Sacramento Business Journal Tia Gemmell Contributing photographer Sacramento Business Journal 11 photos My Sister's House 2015 Art With a Heart fundraiser was held on July 30 at the Vergeâ€¦ more My Sister's House 2015 Art With a Heart fundraiser was held on July 30 at the Verge Center for the Arts . The Asian Pacific Islander Capitol Association and the Sacramento Metro Lions assisted in presenting the event, which benefited victims of domestic violence, sexual assault and human trafficking. The work of artist Sharon Gerber was featured, and attendees were able to make their own artwork at several craft stations.
